-Turkey.
-Chicken salad.

199
02:00:10,980 --> 02:00:13,650
-♪ I got a tofu wrap ♪
-Tofu?!

200
02:00:13,650 --> 02:00:15,720
-Yeah, I'm trying vegan again.

201
02:00:15,720 --> 02:00:18,860
-Ha! Cut to tomorrow
with you with a burger.

202
02:00:18,850 --> 02:00:20,450
-So true.

203
02:00:20,450 --> 02:00:22,190
-Guilty!
-I love that.

204
02:00:23,820 --> 02:00:25,620
-We talkin' lunch?

205
02:00:26,930 --> 02:00:28,630
-What?

206
02:00:28,630 --> 02:00:31,530
-I'm doing homemade nachos.

207
02:00:31,530 --> 02:00:33,800
-God. Kathy's here.

208
02:00:33,800 --> 02:00:36,170
-I didn't even see her come in.

209
02:00:36,170 --> 02:00:37,770
-Do we invite her over?

210
02:00:37,770 --> 02:00:40,070
-Oh, no, no. We cannot.

211
02:00:40,070 --> 02:00:44,010
I wish there was another way
to say this, but I hate her.

212
02:00:44,010 --> 02:00:45,110
-Yeah, me too.

213
02:00:45,110 --> 02:00:46,980
-She's awful.
-She's the worst.

214
02:00:46,980 --> 02:00:50,080
