of these things?

215
02:00:50,080 --> 02:00:51,580
-Nachos?

216
02:00:51,590 --> 02:00:53,860
Yes, we've heard of nachos.

217
02:00:53,850 --> 02:00:55,790
-Okay, Kathy, enjoy your lunch.

218
02:00:55,790 --> 02:00:57,230
-Oh, I will.

219
02:00:57,220 --> 02:00:58,690
Brought these from home.

220
02:00:58,690 --> 02:01:00,390
I'd share with you,
but I crushed up

221
